body_html:

the stuff works fine before and today during the pycharm debugging, the next run pops up the

ImportError: /home/jxu/anaconda3/envs/tf-cpu/lib/python3.6/site-packages/tensorflow/python/_pywrap_tensorflow_internal.so: undefined symbol: _ZN10tensorflow20UnaryDatasetOpKernel11MakeDatasetEPNS_15OpKernelContextEPPNS_11DatasetBaseE

install the tensorflow via pip install tensorflow==1.10.0 or 1.10.1

Regards,

Jian Xu
